# Flutter UI optimization (Vyooo)

Work **one screen/file at a time** until fully migrated before moving to the next.

## Design tokens (required)

| Need | Use | Never |
|------|-----|--------|
| **Typography** | `AppTypography` + `AppFonts` | Inline `fontFamily`, `fontSize`, `fontWeight` |
| Gaps / vertical rhythm | `AppSpacing`, `AppPadding` | `SizedBox(height: 24)` |
| Control / icon dimensions | `AppSizes` | Magic width/height for UI chrome |
| Corner radius | `AppRadius` | `BorderRadius.circular(30)` |
| Gradients | `AppGradients` / `AppGradientBackground` | Inline `LinearGradient` |
| Auth form inset | `AppPadding.authFormHorizontal` | `horizontal: 28` |

Add new values to the token file first; no screen-local layout constants.

## Typography standard (Figma)

**Family:** **DM Sans** everywhere (`AppFonts.body`, `ThemeData.fontFamily`). Bundled weights: **400, 500, 600, 700** only.

| Role | Weight | Size |
|------|--------|------|
| Auth headline | 600 | 30 (−3% letter spacing; use `AppTypography.authHeadline`) |
| Inputs, toggles | 400–500 | 16 |
| Primary button ("Register") | 400 | 20 |
| Footer prompt ("Already have…") | 400 | 12 @ 90% white |
| Footer action ("Sign in") | 700 | 12 |
| Divider ("Or sign up with") | 400 | 10 @ 90% white |

```dart
Text('Create an\nAccount', style: AppTypography.authHeadline);
TextFormField(style: AppTypography.input, ...);
Text('Register', style: AppTypography.primaryButton);
Text('Already have an account? ', style: AppTypography.authSmallBody);
Text('Sign in', style: AppTypography.authSmallBodyBold);
Text('Or sign up with', style: AppTypography.authDividerLabel);
```

Default `ThemeData.fontFamily` is **DM Sans**; use `AppTypography.*` — never **Inter** or inline `fontFamily` on screens.

## Shared widgets

Check `lib/core/widgets/` and `lib/core/widgets/auth/` before duplicating UI.

**Auth fields** — import `auth_widgets.dart`:

- `AuthNameField`, `AuthSurnameField`, `AuthEmailField`, `AuthPhoneField`, `AuthPasswordField`, `AuthLoginIdentifierField`, `AuthUsernameField`
- `AuthRememberForgotRow` — sign-in remember / forgot row
- `AuthFieldColumn` — auto spacing between fields
- Low-level: `AuthUnderlineTextField` for one-off fields

## Auth screen shell

`AppGradientBackground` already applies `SafeArea` — do not nest another.

